90
00:08:08.279 --> 00:08:09.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Esta mísera cosa?

91
00:08:09.489 --> 00:08:12.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
