112
00:09:48.254 --> 00:09:51.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Einar, empuja desde atrás.

113
00:09:51.424 --> 00:09:52.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
