123
00:10:50.232 --> 00:10:51.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Entendido!

124
00:11:00.868 --> 00:11:02.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Vamos.

125
