126
00:11:30.940 --> 00:11:34.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nunca perdonaré a esos tíos.

127
00:11:34.944 --> 00:11:36.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
