137
00:12:13.399 --> 00:12:15.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Pues debe importarte!

138
00:12:16.026 --> 00:12:18.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Somos propiedad del amo!

139
00:12:18.863 --> 00:12:22.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Es inaceptable que unos asistentes
nos exploten.

140
00:12:22.158 --> 00:12:24.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Se lo diré al amo.

141
00:12:25.161 --> 00:12:29.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
